wikipedia_page.main: Sir Henry Winston Barron, 1st Baronet DL (15 October 1795 – 19 April 1872) was an Irish baronet and politician, who stood at nine different general elections.

response: #Hon. Augusta Anne Somerset (21 April 1824 – 27 December 1881), married Sir Henry Barron, 1st Baronet on 1 August 1863.
Rev. Barron's brother Sir Henry Barron, 1st Baronet served as an MP for Waterford City.
*Sir Henry Barron, 1st Baronet (1795–1872), British MP for Waterford City
